Well, it should probably be supported, because otherwise we end up with this sort of thing:
@TemplateExtension
public class MyExtensions {

 public static String foo(String f){}
 public static String bar(String f){}

 @TemplateExtension(matchName = "ANY")
 public static Integer wtf(Integer f, String method){}
}
And I suspect this will break because we will have the same method registered twice, no?
